The paper discusses a machine learning approach to tackle the class imbalance problem in classification tasks. This falls under the domain of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also mentions the use of resampling methods in computer vision (cs.CV) and data science (cs.DS) applications. Additionally, the use of meta-learning techniques is relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
